== Thingfish::MarshalledMetaStore

This is a simple metastore plugin for ThingFish which saves metadata to a single 
serialized hash on disk.

== Configuration

 plugins:
	metastore:
	  name: marshalled
	  root: /tmp/thingfish/metastore

=== Config Keys ===

[name]::
  Set to 'marshalled' to use this plugin.
[root]::
  The directory to store the marshalled metadata in.

